Name: Mission Park
Descritpion: A historical park with a large grassy area and beautiful postel memorial rose garden

Name: Franceschi Park
Descritpion: A “Riviera” neighborhood park with a stunning panoramic view of the City of Santa Barbara and its coastline and a view of the Channel Islands

Name: East Beach Park/Palm Park
Descritpion: A fun park in front of east beach with great tall palm trees and ocean view, and with a long grassy area great for picnics, and a fun bike trail with ocean and park view.
